{\rtf1\ansi \deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fswiss .VnArial;}}{\colortbl;\red0\green0\blue0;\red255\green255\blue255;}\deftab1134\plain \f0 \fs32 \b \pard\qj \sl320 \tab \tab C\'b8ch l\'b5m cho g\'ad\'acng s\'b8ng b\'e3ng\par \plain \f0 \fs24 \par M\'c6t g\'ad\'acng soi c\'e3 m\'b9 m\'e9t l\'edp b\'b9c (tr\'b8ng thu\'fb) kh\'abng ch\'deu \'ae\'ad\'eec n\'ad\'edc. B\'b9n n\'aan treo g\'ad\'acng soi n\'aci kh\'ab r\'b8o v\'b5 nh\'ed \'ae\'f5ng c\'c7m g\'ad\'acng khi tay \'ad\'edt hay \'ae\'c6t g\'ad\'acng g\'c7n n\'ad\'edc n\'e3ng (h\'aci n\'ad\'edc s\'cf l\'b5m m\'ea g\'ad\'acng).\par \par N\'d5u g\'ad\'acng b\'de lu m\'ea, d\'ac b\'c8n, b\'b9n h\'b7y l\'cay kh\'a8n m\'d2m, nh\'f3ng v\'b5o c\'e5n 90 \'ae\'e9 ch\'efi cho m\'c6t g\'ad\'acng s\'b8ng l\'b9i.\par \par Ngo\'b5i ra, b\'b9n c\'e3 th\'d3 d\'efng mai c\'b8 m\'f9c t\'b8n nhuy\'d4n nh\'ad b\'e9t, ch\'d5 v\'b5o m\'e9t \'ddt n\'ad\'edc s\'abicho s\'d2n s\'d6t r\'e5i th\'cam n\'ad\'edc n\'b5y thoa \'ae\'d2u l\'aan m\'c6t g\'ad\'acng. \'a7\'d3 nh\'ad v\'cby qua m\'e9t \'ae\'aam, sau \'ae\'e3 d\'efng kh\'a8n s\'b9ch lau l\'b9i cho b\'e3ng.\par \par N\'aan nh\'ed, ph\'b6i d\'efng kh\'a8n m\'d2m \'ae\'d3 lau g\'ad\'acng, k\'ceo g\'ad\'acng b\'de tr\'c7y x\'ad\'edc.\par \par Tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep g\'ad\'acng soi hay c\'f6a k\'ddnh b\'de hoen \'e8, b\'b9n c\'e3 th\'d3 l\'cay m\'e9t mi\'d5ng gi\'ce b\'e4c m\'e9t d\'f3m mu\'e8i, nh\'f3ng n\'ad\'edc h\'aci \'ad\'edt r\'e5i ch\'b5 l\'aan m\'c6t k\'ddnh (g\'ad\'acng), sau \'ae\'e3 d\'efng kh\'a8n s\'b9ch lau kh\'ab l\'b9i, k\'ddnh (g\'ad\'acng) s\'cf s\'b8ng lo\'b8ng nh\'ad m\'edi.}